      <title>法国央行预测今年最后几个月经济将零增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/bank-of-france-predicts-zero-growth-in-final-months-of-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行预计，尽管前三个月法国经济受到巴黎奥运会的推动，且政治局势继续加剧商业不确定性，但第四季度法国经济将陷入停滞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/bank-of-france-predicts-zero-growth-in-final-months-of-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
