      <title>南非发行 1922 年以来首笔美元债券，筹资 35 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/south-africa-markets-eurobonds-after-coalition-lifts-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非自 2022 年以来首次发行美元债券，需求强劲，表明人们对 5 月大选后组建的联合政府充满信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/south-africa-markets-eurobonds-after-coalition-lifts-confidence</guid>
